helps relieve excessive tension in the musculoskeletal corset of the spine;
helps get rid of pain in the back, lower back, shoulders, and neck;
improves blood and lymph circulation during the massage;
restores elasticity and tone of muscles, ligaments, and fascia;
used as part of rehabilitation for spinal diseases and injuries;
